    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genus of Old World sparrows that are found naturally in open habitats in the warmer climates of Africa and southern Eurasia, including several species that have adapted to human habitation.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
